The Blood War is the eternal struggle between the races of the Lower Planes. Among the most prominent races involved in the conflict are the Baatezu, Tanar'ri and the Yugoloths. 
Major battlefields of the war include the Field of Nettles in the Gray+Wastes; Moldrus'+Gap, the Stones of Draetilus, the Scarlet Jungle and the Stinging Sands of Minethys in Carceri; the Burning Glacier of Mungoth, Death's Gorge and the Bridge of Khalas in Gehenna; and the Walls+of+Corristro in the Abyss. 

